KILL: Initiate combat with a target

Syntax: kill <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Begins combat with the specified target. You must be in the same room.
  Once combat starts, your character attacks automatically each melee round
  using your available Attacks Per Melee (APM).

  You cannot kill other players in most areas (PK rules apply).
  Non-aggressive NPCs will fight back if attacked.

EXAMPLE:
  kill bandit

SEE ALSO: flee, stop, autododge, autoparry, combat
